text:
@samsunggulf This has been the worst service experience I have ever had. I am extremely disappointed with this brand and the customer service, especially Hager Ramadan.
I bought a dryer two weeks ago and used it only twice. The first time was fine, but the second time it showed an error and stopped working, and no one has been able to fix it.

On top of that, the delivery was delayed from 23/02 to 27/02 without even asking me. The customer service specialist did nothing to address my frustration or escalate the issue to a duty manager to arrange a visit tomorrow.

My clothes are still wet and will be damaged if this continues. This level of service is unacceptable.
Shame on this brand. I truly regret buying this product.#
@carrefouruae your products quality is very poor quality

